author: Fextralife
description:
Hell is Us Review
In this Hell is Us review. I'm going to be talking about the new action role palying title or action adventure title from Rogue Factor that is available to play today. If you have the Deluxe edition of the game, but will be coming out on September 4th. If you don't I'm going to be talking about the story setting, gameplay, the graphics and the performance of the game, and ultimately whether you should spend you money on this game right now or should wait until later, or maybe not even play it at all.
